    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">This is a simple to use 7 in 1 waterproof survival multi-purpose whistle! With camping season just around the corner, it&#039;s a great time to teach your children the basic camping and survival skills that have been handed down to you by your parents, their parents, and of course the Boy Scouts. This multi-use whistle is the start to good preparation and essential outdoor safety. Each whistle features 7 functions - whistle, magnifier, flashlight, storage container, compass, thermometer and a signaling mirror. The plastic body is a bright orange color to improve visibility and it comes with a lanyard so you can easily hang it around your neck, on your belt or your backpack. Make sure to grab a few of these before your next camping trip!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Kids Survival Outdoor Camping Multi Tool Whistle Compass LED 7 in 1 Flashlight</h2>\n  <p>This is a simple to use 7 in 1 waterproof survival multi-purpose whistle!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>Thermometer (Fahrenheit &amp; Celsius)</li>\n    <li>5x Magnifier | Signal Mirror</li>\n    <li>LED Flashlight | Storage Compartment</li>\n    <li>Safety Whistle | Compass</li>\n    <li>Teach Kids About Outdoor Camping and Hiking Safety</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/camping_hiking/CCH7-1_7in1_survival_whistle_GRN_detail_01.jpg\" alt=\"This is a simple to use 7 in 1 waterproof survival multi-purpose whistle\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> SON71EW</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 808533533459</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>With camping season just around the corner, it&#039;s a great time to teach your children the basic camping and survival skills that have been handed down to you by your parents, their parents, and of course the Boy Scouts.</p>\n  <p>This multi-use whistle is the start to good preparation and essential outdoor safety. Each whistle features 7 functions - whistle, magnifier, flashlight, storage container, compass, thermometer and a signaling mirror. The plastic body is a bright orange color to improve visibility and it comes with a lanyard so you can easily hang it around your neck, on your belt or your backpack. Make sure to grab a few of these before your next camping trip!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "This is a simple to use 7 in 1 waterproof survival multi-purpose whistle! With camping season just around the corner, it's a great time to teach your children the basic camping and survival skills that have been handed down to you by your parents, their parents, and of course the Boy Scouts. This multi-use whistle is the start to good preparation and essential outdoor safety. Each whistle features 7 functions - whistle, magnifier, flashlight, storage container, compass, thermometer and a signaling mirror. The plastic body is a bright orange color to improve visibility and it comes with a lanyard so you can easily hang it around your neck, on your belt or your backpack. Make sure to grab a few of these before your next camping trip!.",
